anding Page.\",\"is_featured\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p>Ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi d&ugrave;ng khi truy c\\u1eadp website, th\\u01b0\\u1eddng click v&agrave;o r\\u1ea5t nhi\\u1ec1u th&ocirc;ng tin kh&aacute;c nhau tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc khi t&igrave;m \\u0111\\u1ebfn m\\u1ee5c ti&ecirc;u h\\u1ecd c\\u1ea7n. Trong khi \\u0111&oacute;, ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi d&ugrave;ng s\\u1ebd t&igrave;m \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ngay \\u0111\\u1ebfn m\\u1ee5c ti&ecirc;u h\\u1ecd c\\u1ea7n khi truy c\\u1eadp Landing Page.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h5><strong>PH\\u1ea6N 1: LANDING PAGE L&Agrave; G&Igrave;?<\\/strong><\\/h5>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>M\\u1ed9t c&aacute;ch ng\\u1eafn g\\u1ecdn v&agrave; \\u0111\\u1ea7y \\u0111\\u1ee7: &ldquo;Trong c&aacute;c chi\\u1ebfn d\\u1ecbch qu\\u1ea3ng c&aacute;o tr\\u1ef1c tuy\\u1ebfn, Landing Page l&agrave; m\\u1ed9t trang web \\u0111\\u01a1n c&oacute; n\\u1ed9i dung t\\u1eadp trung nh\\u1eb1m d\\u1eabn d\\u1eaft v&agrave; thuy\\u1ebft ph\\u1ee5c ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi \\u0111\\u1ecdc th\\u1ef1c hi\\u1ec7n m\\u1ed9t m\\u1ee5c ti&ecirc;u chuy\\u1ec3n \\u0111\\u1ed5i c\\u1ee5 th\\u1ec3.&rdquo;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>V\\u1eady, LANDING PAGE th\\u01b0\\u1eddng c&oacute; c&aacute;c d\\u1ea1ng nh\\u01b0 th\\u1ebf n&agrave;o, m\\u1ee5c \\u0111&iacute;ch v&agrave; \\u0111\\u1eb7c \\u0111i\\u1ec3m c\\u1ee7a ch&uacute;ng ra sao? B&agrave;i sau m&igrave;nh s\\u1ebd \\u0111i c\\u1ee5 th\\u1ec3 v&agrave;o 3 d\\u1ea1ng th\\u01b0\\u1eddng g\\u1eb7p nh\\u1ea5t nh&eacute;.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>C&oacute; 3 d\\u1ea1ng landing page ph\\u1ed5 bi\\u1ebfn d\\u1ef1a theo m\\u1ee5c ti&ecirc;u chuy\\u1ec3n \\u0111\\u1ed5i:<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"padding-left:30px;\\\"><em>+ Landing Page thu th\\u1eadp kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng ti\\u1ec1m n\\u0103ng<\\/em><br \\/>\\r\\n<em>+ Landing Page B&aacute;n h&agrave;ng<\\/em><br \\/>\\r\\n<em>+ Landing Page Trung gian chuy\\u1ec3n \\u0111\\u1ed5i<\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong>Landing Page thu th\\u1eadp kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng ti\\u1ec1m n\\u0103ng (LEAD GENERATION PAGE):<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"margin-left:40px;\\\">M\\u1ee5c ti&ecirc;u: Thu th\\u1eadp nh\\u1eefng th&ocirc;ng tin c\\u01a1 b\\u1ea3n c\\u1ee7a kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng ti\\u1ec1m n\\u0103ng (nh\\u01b0 h\\u1ecd t&ecirc;n, email, s\\u1ed1 \\u0111i\\u1ec7n tho\\u1ea1i) \\u0111\\u1ec3 s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng cho c&aacute;c ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng marketing sau \\u0111&oacute;.<br \\/>\\r\\n\\u0110\\u1eb7c \\u0111i\\u1ec3m: Thu th\\u1eadp th&ocirc;ng tin b\\u1eb1ng m\\u1ed9t bi\\u1ec3u m\\u1eabu \\u0111\\u0103ng k&yacute; v&agrave; lu&ocirc;n \\u0111i k&egrave;m v\\u1edbi m\\u1ed9t l\\u1ee3i &iacute;ch trao \\u0111\\u1ed5i v\\u1edbi kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng nh\\u01b0 ebook, webinar, h\\u1ed9i th\\u1ea3o offline, t\\u01b0 v\\u1ea5n mi\\u1ec5n ph&iacute;, qu&agrave; t\\u1eb7ng, m&atilde; gi\\u1ea3m gi&aacute;&hellip;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong>Landing Page B&aacute;n h&agrave;ng (SALES PAGE)<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"margin-left:40px;\\\">M\\u1ee5c ti&ecirc;u: Thuy\\u1ebft ph\\u1ee5c kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng \\u0111\\u01b0a ra quy\\u1ebft \\u0111\\u1ecbnh mua h&agrave;ng ngay tr&ecirc;n Landing Page.<br \\/>\\r\\n\\u0110\\u1eb7c \\u0111i\\u1ec3m: N\\u1ed9i dung v\\u1ec1 s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m\\/d\\u1ecbch v\\u1ee5 \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c x&acirc;y d\\u1ef1ng chi ti\\u1ebft bao g\\u1ed3m: l\\u1ee3i &iacute;ch kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng, \\u0111\\u1eb7c \\u0111i\\u1ec3m n\\u1ed5i b\\u1eadt, ph\\u1ea3n h\\u1ed3i kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng, b\\u1ea3ng gi&aacute;, ch&iacute;nh s&aacute;ch&hellip;, gi&uacute;p kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng c&oacute; \\u0111\\u1ea7y \\u0111\\u1ee7 th&ocirc;ng tin \\u0111\\u1ec3 \\u0111\\u01b0a ra quy\\u1ebft \\u0111\\u1ecbnh mua h&agrave;ng.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong>Landing Page Trung gian chuy\\u1ec3n \\u0111\\u1ed5i (CLICK-THROUGH PAGE)<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"margin-left:40px;\\\">M\\u1ee5c ti&ecirc;u: D\\u1eabn d\\u1eaft ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi \\u0111\\